h that the accretion rate no longer reaches the level required to\ntrigger a transition. Finally, we highlight similarities between disk winds in\nHLX-1 and in the Galactic black hole V404 Cyg.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Apr 2017 18:00:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-31"}
