fects the\nisotope ratios of product ions only. The chlorine isotopologues of the observed\nprecursor ions are deduced to never obey binomial distribution, regardless of\nwhat modes of the initial isotopologue distributions of the total precursor\nions are.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Apr 2017 04:24:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Jul 2017 13:17:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-05"}
